Build a Streamlit app named support_dashboard.

Goal:
Create a small UI for Support Intelligence Copilot.

Requirements:
- Use Streamlit
- Import analyze_ticket_risk from ticket_risk_analyzer
- Import generate_next_best_action from next_best_action_generator
- The UI should contain:
  - app title and short description
  - text area for support ticket text
  - text input for account name
  - numeric input for ARR
  - text input for renewal date
  - select box for customer tier: SMB, Mid-Market, Enterprise
  - Analyze button

When the user clicks Analyze:
- run ticket_risk_analyzer
- run next_best_action_generator
- show results in clearly separated sections/cards:
  - risk summary
  - key detected signals
  - revenue impact
  - next best actions
  - stakeholders to involve
  - escalation recommendation
  - executive reply draft
  - internal notes

Design expectations:
- clean, minimal, polished
- readable headings
- no external database
- just local execution

Also generate any minimal helper/example file if needed.
